scene_description_enriched: The image depicts a figure representing Sagittarius, the zodiac sign. The figure has the upper body of a human with long blond hair, wearing a striped tunic. The lower body is that of a centaur, with a horse's hindquarters and a tail. The figure is holding a drawn bow and arrow, aiming to the left. The setting is an outdoor landscape with rolling green hills and a few indistinct buildings in the background. The scene is framed by a decorative border.
